b8524a319a23cB2bd6f79b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" targ=
et=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bo=
rder-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: =
solid; background-color: #ccc;">noted last month</a>, though other bets can=
 lead to suspicions of manipulation. Other sports sometimes have <a href=3D=
"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34337106.258392/aHR0cHM6Ly93=
d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDItMDUvbWFyay16dWNrZXJ=
