GFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB240247b6" itemprop=3D"StoryL=
ink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; tex=
t-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-colo=
r: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  stricter=
 rules</a> about insider betting, but <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
