<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And people who set up=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://=
link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34337106.258392/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY=
29tL2NvbnRlbnQvOTEwOGYzOTMtNmE0NS00MWEzLWJkNzYtMjA1ODFiMTkyODhl/607f07ceef4=
